---
import worldSVG from "../../svgs/earth_line.svg"
import codeSVG from "../../svgs/code_fill.svg"
import handSVG from "../../svgs/hand_heart_line.svg"
import pinSVG from "../../svgs/pin_fill.svg"
import cupSVG from "../../svgs/teacup_line.svg"
---

<div
  class="lg:items-begin my-16 flex flex-col items-center justify-center"
>
    <h1
      class="mb-8 text-center text-5xl font-bold text-partner-text dark:text-dnt-orange-400"
    >
      Partnerships
    </h1>
    <div class = "flex flex-col items-baseline align-center w-5/6 justify-between md:flex-row">
      <div class ="flex flex-col items-center justify-center" id="connect">
        <img
        src={worldSVG}
        alt="SVG of the world"
        >
        <p class="w-2/3 mt-5">
          Make meaningfull <span class="text-partner-text">connections</span> by becoming our partner.
          From students to businesses, you will increase the network of your organization.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class ="flex flex-col items-center justify-center" id="give">
        <img
        src={handSVG}
        alt="SVG representing giving"
        >
        <p class="w-2/3 mt-5">
          By becoming our partner, you <span class="text-partner-text">invest</span> in innovation, research and education.
          Together we will achieve better <span class="text-partner-text">education</span>, work on <span class="text-partner-text">research</span> and <span class="text-partner-text">innovate</span> in the field of robotics.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class ="flex flex-col items-center justify-center" id="code">
        <img
        src={codeSVG}
        alt="SVG of code"
        >
        <p class="w-2/3 mt-5">
          Technology is the basis of our society. In collaberating with us,
          your organization will support new <span class="text-partner-text">technologies</span>
          that can change our way of living.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class ="flex flex-col items-center justify-center" id="pin">
        <img
        src={pinSVG}
        alt="SVG of the world"
        >
        <p class="w-2/3 mt-5">
          Put your organization in the <span class="text-partner-text">spot-light</span> at
          important events. Make sure the name of your organization is known accross the sector of
          <span class="text-partner-text">robotics</span> by collaberating with us.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  <!-- <img src="/images/Team_Complete.webp" width="800px" alt="DNT team image" /> -->
</div>

<div
  class="bg-white lg:items-begin flex flex-col items-center justify-center pt-10"
>
    <h1
      class="mb-4 text-center text-5xl font-bold dark:text-dnt-orange-400"
    >
      Interested?
    </h1>
    <div class="mb-3 flex items-center">
      <h3
        class="text-center text-3xl dark:text-dnt-orange-400 mr-3"
      >
        Hit us up for a cup of coffee.
      </h3>
      <img
        src={cupSVG}
        alt="SVG of a cup"
        width="42"
        >
    </div>
    <p class="mb-16 text-center text-xl dark:text-dnt-orange-400 text-partner-text inline-block	">partnerships@dutchnaoteam.nl </p>
  <!-- <img src="/images/Team_Complete.webp" width="800px" alt="DNT team image" /> -->
</div>
